{"tid":217978,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【蟲蟲救地球】或成塑膠污染救星，科學家發現蠟蟲能吃膠袋","createTime":"2017-04-26T07:32:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-26T08:10:54.000Z","uid":64858,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cec34913a2bfae51512684b688574eec9e0a2239","tid":217978,"uid":64858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T07:32:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://techstart.presslogic.com/2017/04/26/article/24528/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftechstart.presslogic.com%2F2017%2F04%2F26%2Farticle%2F24528%2F&d=aJB%2Bq6ruafnyRbkwc%2FW5ZosQCuff2cTRbXvS6e969MQ%3D&h=0165e01c\" target=\"_blank\">http://techstart.presslogic.com/2017/04/26/article/24528/</a><br />\n塑膠污染的問題或許要靠「蟲蟲特攻隊」來解決？西班牙科學家日前發現，蠟蛾幼蟲竟然能夠吃掉膠袋，或成解決塑膠廢物污染的關鍵。<br />\n <br />\n蠟蛾幼蟲一直以來因為會吃掉及破壞蜂巢而被視為害蟲。西班牙一位科學家在家中清除蜂巢中的蠟蛾幼蟲後，將之置於膠袋內封好，沒多久後它們卻咬穿膠袋「逃走」了&mdash;&mdash;因此意外發現這些幼蟲竟然能夠吃膠袋。<br />\n<br />\n於是這位科學家便與研究團隊一同研究蠟蛾幼蟲這項「特異功能」。實驗中，他們將百條蠟蛾幼蟲與膠袋放在一起12小時，結果幼蟲足足舌食了92毫克膠袋中的聚乙烯，膠袋支離破碎。團隊解釋，蜂蠟的化學結構與膠袋中的聚乙烯接近，因此蠟蛾幼蟲吃膠袋其實是天性使然。<br />\n<br />\n研究人員表示，未來將會進一步研究提取蠟蛾幼蟲內用作消化塑膠的酵素，亦指出這次發現或有助尋找解決塑膠廢物的辦法，減輕對環境的污染。<br />\n<br />\nSource: Science Alert<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ae63e8fca2495677c8b6f3a50b2d161aa6fb583","tid":217978,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T08:01:21.000Z","msg":"嘩。膠都食到"},{"pid":"01c5a8ee28eaaa4175be91d4025f61dd0aa34a21","tid":217978,"uid":11148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T08:05:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>嘩。膠都食到</blockquote><br />\n最勁係消化到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64286943deeb2502b25aa625d396e862cbcb69e9","tid":217978,"uid":82532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T08:08:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05256a9621c9e6397fc649ce092a39faab328e0f","tid":217978,"uid":109077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T08:10:54.000Z","msg":"我記得麵包蟲都得<br />\n細細個比膠袋佢食佢真係食"}]}